    <briefdescription>
<para>Parameters for setting data for a specific periodic advertising with response subevent. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This struct provides the necessary information to set the data for a specific subevent in a Periodic Advertising with Response (PAwR) scenario. It specifies the subevent number, the range of response slots to listen to, and the actual data to send. This is used to respond to data request from an advertiser by sending back the data in the specified subevent.</para>
<para><simplesect kind="note"><para>Used in <ref refid="group__bt__gap_1ga7de30fe5040b85bb9212e3a8fec4ac45" kindref="member">bt_le_per_adv_set_subevent_data</ref> function. </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
    </detaileddescription>
